# CODEOWNERS — RisqBase UI Components
#
# Routes path-scoped reviews to @fiadeleke (CEO) — the only real GitHub
# handle on the team for now. The path-specific rules are kept (rather
# than collapsed to `* @fiadeleke`) so we can expand individual paths
# to other team members as they come on board with GH accounts.
#
# Note: this file is currently informational — the Main ruleset on `main`
# has `require_code_owner_review: false`. Switch that on once handles
# diversify if you want CODEOWNERS to gate reviews.
#
# Format: <path> <space-separated owner handles>
# Last matching pattern wins; later rules override earlier ones.

# Design tokens (TS source)
src/tokens/**         @fiadeleke

# Data visualisation primitives
src/data-viz/**       @fiadeleke

# AI surface components
src/ai/**             @fiadeleke

# Documentation site (MDX content + meta)
docs/**               @fiadeleke

# Raw token sources (Style Dictionary input — design + engineering joint owners)
tokens/**             @fiadeleke
